5:
Wow, you're good! It looks like the
real thing!
7:
You want me to draw something?
Hmm...
10:
Here you go! A bunny! What do you
think?
21:
There's so much here, but also
nothing at all. All this stuff, and no
one else is here? This place is so...
25:
I have to paint it... Or else I'll forget it
all!
32:
It looks like I managed to pull you
out. Are you okay, Ryouki?
39:
Wait, who you are isn't important. I
need to go back and—
43:
Are you trying to throw your life
away? You'll vanish into nothingness
if you go in your current condition.
47:
Hold on... You were with Kugui
before...
50:
But... who's Kugui? Were they...
someone to me?
55:
It's okay. Everything will come back
to you when you wake up.
59:
We can see Kugui after this. I'll meet
you once we return to the real world.
67: Wh-what the heck is all this?!
81:
...You now possess the same power
as Kugui.
89:
I wouldn't be in such a hurry to
celebrate. Don't you realize the
danger you're in?
93:
I'm sure you remember how
unstable my power has been
throughout my life.
101:
There's also another matter to be
concerned about. How much do you
recall about your dream?
105:
Er... There was shiny stuff scattered
everywhere? But it was also super
dark...
109:
You artists are all the same...
Capable of forming new possibilities
from within yourself.
111:
Kugui has no doubt influenced you
as well. In short, you connected to
somewhere you shouldn't have.
113:
Without Couette, your very essence
would have been melted away, into
the unknown. You owe her your life.
117:
I had no idea it was that bad...
Thanks, Couette.
120: I know this is a bad time to ask, but...
124:
Do you know a way for me to paint
what I saw?
127:
I-I don't know why, but... I want to do
it. I feel compelled to.
130:
It was like... all that we could
possibly ever know was there! I just—
134:
It's okay, Ryouki. I'll be with you every
step of the way. I intended to do so
from the beginning.
138:
Whatever path you decide to tread, I
only hope you properly prepare
yourself for it.
142:
That sounds like permission to me!
Let's do it, Kugui!
147:
I'll help, too. I've got experience in
this field.
152:
We'll be counting on your expertise,
then!
157:
Ryouki, try pouring your power
into this.
162:
Is this a protective charm? But how
do I use my power...
167:
Wh-whoa! These guys just popped
up outta nowhere!
171:
They're your shikigami, Ryouki. They'll
help you out when you use your
power.
175:
Hey, these guys are the oni from
before, aren't they? Wow! They look
so cute now!
179:
We'll take you to a place you can
train at.
189:
Am I not gonna train here at the
commission?
200:
You were training here all this time,
Kugui?
204:
If only I could've come sooner! This is
awesome!
213:
I sure am! And you must be Alk's
little sis, right?
217:
That's right! I'm Nao Nagihara! Nice
to meet you.
224:
No, everything's fine. I just wanted to
ask... Are you having fun right now?
228:
You bet I am! I'm so excited, my
heart's pounding in my chest!
231:
...I've gotta draw all sorts of stuff I
never have before if I wanna be able
to paint that world.
235:
So that's exactly what I'll do. I'm
going to commit everything I see
from now on to paper!
